/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒裸條又係好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喇沙同新加坡/香港唔一樣 仲有個rojak炒通菜/水果都好值得試<br />\n花生冰又係好好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你夠膽既可以去埋啲馬拉人既市集 <br />\n不過呢個啲嘢食就一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/185738_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F185738_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=de12d8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/185758_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F185758_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ae65ce04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/185824_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F185824_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1fe9f5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/185845_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F185845_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=878973fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩果part就真係唔知 我都係行下商場同去蛇廟同古廟<br />\n但嘢食真係每次都有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca5949f5fc1db55f16dc8ff5973eee4e7c78628","tid":566080,"uid":39785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c8b44c52fc46c683496b9977108347e4429e9d","tid":566080,"uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T10:59:58.000Z","msg":"正wo <